name: dying at buffalo wild wings
description: eat barely cooked wings. drink a hot blue moon poured by xanax faced employee who attempts to convert you to scientology. root on your favorite team and consider your impotence. let your tears mix with the mountain dew code red sauce that spill over your indiscernible bowl of flesh like loose bowels from the neglected toilet. leave your arm as a tip. for the great service. and die at buffalo wild wings.
